Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:31.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnFOT-Gospel Std EB\blur0.6\pos(960,750)\fs200\fscx110\b1\c&H33A950&}To be continued
Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Sports!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When considering popular demand, \NI settled on these cast members.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no "demand" for these.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.33,0:00:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I've been chosen by this "popular demand."
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.08,0:00:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Elma, you're standing in for Lucoa.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This segment is about sports.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.34,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna, you just keep things rolling along, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get things going!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.67,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.59,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Soccer!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(26,359,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Soccer!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna, pass!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no you don't!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.73,0:00:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Disqualified!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't like that!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just put your horn away.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.81,0:00:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.15,0:00:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(24,358,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Volleyball!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Tohru!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.03,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no you don't!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the net.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.12,0:01:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, just put your horn away.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Swimming!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.33,0:01:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(25,359,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Swimming!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is my territory! \NNo one can beat me at this!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why, you...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,[cps2],Why does this keep happening?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.72,0:01:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, your horn...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.76,0:01:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.09,0:01:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Elma is a fool.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.64,0:01:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kendo!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.89,0:01:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(25,359,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Kendo!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.40,0:01:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Horn!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.19,0:01:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Point!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Horns don't count!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.86,0:01:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Horn!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.65,0:01:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Point!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just...!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.86,0:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are human sports all so difficult?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For the last time, \Nif you put your horn away...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.87,0:01:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheerleading!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(25,359,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Cheerleader!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.96,0:01:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, I found a sport that I can do!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.17,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this accomplish?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind getting down, already?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Elma?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your time to shine!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.64,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Elma, you're so cool.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you insist, then I guess I can keep this up.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical duh-ragon.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.31,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it for\NMiss Kobayashi's Dragon Sports.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see you again next time.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, wrap it up...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Elma, now's the time to really tough it out!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's cheering for you!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You really blow me away, Elma.